{"tid":586393,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要買動物？？？","createTime":"2018-03-09T13:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T02:51:36.000Z","uid":171706,"like":12,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ac98d1fe471faea8f2ab7a115d6af0e379feb47f","tid":586393,"uid":171706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T13:06:23.000Z","msg":"本少？貪刺激？覺得可以找佢揾一桶金？<br />\n<br />\n成日抱住可以一野赢勁多既心態，認為自已係神，又諗住之後會用贏既錢轉玩正股(未去到呢個stage已輸咗勁多)。但事實係你亦然會用你靠動物贏既錢繼續玩動物，然後就輸錢，之後又唔gur想番身，點知就繼續輸，連本都輸曬。<br />\n<br />\n又或者本身諗住買少少玩下，但係貪心越買越大，以為自已好L準，之後咪又係輸！！<br />\n<br />\n唔信？睇下出面幾多on9係到叫春就知，重要係買得幾千蚊我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n玩動物一係你all in or nothing(但係你點會呀🙊)，不論輸贏都收手。<br />\n長玩一定輸！！"},{"pid":"15ee3c1788391fb28a77637b9eb87b5c6373cb4b","tid":586393,"uid":57308,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T13:14:08.000Z","msg":"得幾千蚊 all in又得罪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63e137f6a198f08a51f93377cbb34f6f4accd95","tid":586393,"uid":81150,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T13:14:46.000Z","msg":"我依家好撚後悔呀屌!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n但訓撚哂身啦點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c777b976285e8f01600a4817d137e9932dfc7b","tid":586393,"uid":81150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15ee3c1788391fb28a77637b9eb87b5c6373cb4b","tid":586393,"uid":57308,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T13:14:08.000Z","msg":"得幾千蚊 all in又得罪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T13:15:12.000Z","msg":"馬清<br />\n<br />\n你咁快手呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b64439aa4a9a51c95360c522ae1da605b28d73","tid":586393,"uid":57308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco